_sText:
I have new bhop map for you.

I have put more time into this one map than my others.
So I hope you'd enjoy it.

Info:
______________________________
This map is probably best for beginners,
since it is remelig easy for normal bhoppers.

But you may well try it, for my sake.


More info:

There are up to 16 players in this map.
You start as T, with a normal gloch and knife.
